<div class="container narrow margin-y-4">
    <p>
        On <code>.accordion__button</code>, set the <code>aria-expanded</code> attribute to
        <code>"true"</code> (Figure 3, line 6). On the related <code>.accordion__panel</code>
        selector, include the class <code>.show</code> (Figure 3, line 11).
    </p>
</div>
